snippet.title: Dauntless | Next-Gen Trailer
snippet.description:
Dauntless launches natively on PlayStation 5, Xbox Series X, and Xbox Series S on December 2. Experience seamless cross-generation support, stunning high-resolution visuals, faster load times, and more.

Play Dauntless for free on Playstation 5, PlayStation 4, Xbox Series X, Xbox Series S, Xbox One, Nintendo Switch, and the Epic Games store with true cross-play and cross-progression. | http://www.playdauntless.com
